We are Almost SOLD OUT! We have a few spot available for the guys - come down and Speed Date with 20 Beautiful Ladies tonight! Get your ticket at www.CTMatch.com or call (860) 236-3343 to reserve your spot

 

♥♥THURSDAY FEB 14 -Valentines SPEED Match Dating Ages 21-41 at Whole Foods, West Hartford Center♥♥

“ Speed Dating is a very inexpensive, efficient and fun way to meet other local singles and go on dates with the people that you want to date”

THIS EVENT SOLD OLD LAST YEAR!
Most of our SPEED Match Daters come from outside of Meetup.com, so the registered Meetup people are a small portion of the people you will meet.

Meet someone SPECIAL on Valentines Day with CTMatch.com and Whole Foods with Valentines SPEED Match Dating

Love is in the air – who will you meet at SPEED Match Dating?

SPEED Match Dating gives you up to 20 5-minute mini-dates – then you choose your matches.

Your matches are emailed to you after the event so you can choose you next dates.

All you information is kept confidential – making SPEED Match Dating the safest and most fun way to meet new people!

FREE Gourmet Appetizers and hors d’ouvres provide by Whole Foods

Appetizers, Registration and seating start at 6:30pm

SPEED Match Dating starts at 7pm


 Whole Foods Market
50 Raymond Rd
West Hartford, CT 06107
West Hartford Center

SEATING IS LIMITED – RESERVE YOUR SPOT TODAY

Tickets are $40 at the event
